It wouldn't be a funeral,</i>

15:19.601 --> 15:21.280
<i>but it would be as much fun as one.</i>

15:29.233 --> 15:30.518
<i>So that evening,</i>

15:30.638 --> 15:33.079
<i>we arrived at the house
of the girl Simon had always loved</i>

15:33.199 --> 15:35.953
<i>and we were drunk, so very drunk.</i>

15:36.073 --> 15:37.123
- Hi.
- Hi.

15:37.243 --> 15:39.700
