- Hello, William.

15:40.326 --> 15:42.076
You coming in then, Simon?

15:43.187 --> 15:44.489
Are you his chaperone?

15:44.650 --> 15:47.145
No, babes.
He's gonna watch the kid while we chat

15:47.265 --> 15:49.129
about, you know, our feelings.

15:50.596 --> 15:53.250
- Best not to call me babes though.
- Really?

15:53.512 --> 15:54.330
Really.

15:55.601 --> 15:58.331
Come on in then.
Chris is watching TV, Will.

15:59.226 --> 16:01.498
Come on, you, let's get a drink.

16:02.889 --> 16:06.026
So Dad went totally ballistic
about the driveway.

16:06.324 --> 16:08.394
I think you're still invited over
for Christmas

16:08.514 --> 16:11.644
but he's gonna make your parents pay
for an industrial stone cleaner.

16:12.473 --> 16:15.210
- It was worth it.
- Can you smell bleach?

16:18.010 --> 16:19.723
- What are you watching?
- Don't know.

16:19.843 --> 16:22.011
- I think there's been a big bomb.
- Really?

16:22.131 --> 16:25.009
Oh, it's one of those recreations
of a dirty bomb.

16:25.171 --> 16:26.609
What's a dirty bomb?

16:26.877 --> 16:29.145
It's just a big nuclear bomb

16:29.265 --> 16:31.609
that terrorists would use to kill
everyone in London.

16:34.138 --> 16:36.169
Have you been drinking spirits?

16:37.137 --> 16:39.609
