Would you like some?

16:39.866 --> 16:42.769
- I'll stick to wine, thanks.
- Wine is for girls.

16:42.889 --> 16:45.339
- I am a girl.
- This is a man's drink.

16:45.459 --> 16:47.021
If you don't want it, I'll have it.

16:47.141 --> 16:50.129
And if you can't take me like this,
well I'm sorry, babes,

16:50.291 --> 16:52.393
but this is the package.

16:57.227 --> 16:59.080
There goes the tallest building
in London.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.704
That'll be a few thousand dead.

17:00.824 --> 17:03.929
My mum and dad are in London tonight.
Would they be killed?

17:04.329 --> 17:06.930
Not only killed but obliterated.

17:07.390 --> 17:09.449
Merely a scorched shadow
on the pavement.

17:09.782 --> 17:10.519
Dust.

17:10.638 --> 17:13.770
- So they are dead forever?
- Yes, dead forever.

17:14.642 --> 17:16.296
My mummy!

17:16.415 --> 17:18.386
My daddy!

17:20.530 --> 17:21.768
Come on, Carli.

17:21.887 --> 17:23.564
You know why I'm here.

17:23.950 --> 17:25.661
And I know why I'm here.

17:27.637 --> 17:29.049
And you know why I'm here.

17:30.491 --> 17:32.729
- Kiss me.
- You know I've got a boyfriend.

17:32.891 --> 17:36.089
- Just finger yourself in front of me.
- Jesus, Simon!

17:36.251 --> 17:39.601
They do it in Caravan Club.
Come on, I know you want to.

17:39.721 --> 17:42.521
- Well I don't want to, so...
- Yeah, you do.

17:44.200 --> 17:46.031
Simon, are you all right?

17:52.549 --> 17:53.653
Oh, Christ.

18:02.006 --> 18:03.409
I don't think I'm very well.

18:03.961 --> 18:06.009
- Daddy! Mummy!
- Chris?

18:09.235 --> 18:12.080
I'm really sorry. I was just telling him
about terrorists and stuff.

18:12.200 --> 18:14.409
You were telling a seven-year-old
about terrorists?

18:14.577 --> 18:17.127
He won't sleep for a week now,
you idiot.

18:17.247 --> 18:19.409
Have you unblocked the sink yet?
All the lumps?

18:19.529 --> 18:20.809
I am really sorry.

18:20.970 --> 18:22.569
I think maybe I ate something.

18:23.530 --> 18:26.266
Could we maybe sit down
and talk about us?

18:26.386 --> 18:29.240
Have you got any Nurofen? It's just...

18:33.930 --> 18:34.975
Oh dear.

18:37.890 --> 18:39.609
I think we'll be off now.

18:40.564 --> 18:43.393
Right, I think we'd better get you
back to mine and cleaned up.

18:43.513 --> 18:45.308
Oh, God, my head.

18:46.517 --> 18:47.827
I've ruined it.

18:49.229 --> 18:52.278
I love her and I've ruined it with her.
Oh, God.

18:52.571 --> 18:54.250
She's so amazing.

18:54.410 --> 18:56.204
I'm going to say this
to you as a friend.

18:56.324 --> 18:57.844
Shut up.

18:58.087 --> 18:59.969
Today's been a fuck-up
from start to finish.

19:00.139 --> 19:02.646
We need to write it off, OK?
Today's gone.

19:02.766 --> 19:04.816
It isn't going to get any worse.

19:06.462 --> 19:08.811
Oh, shit. Isn't that your mum's car?

19:10.515 --> 19:12.365
And that's Neil's dad's car.

19:13.231 --> 19:14.325
Oh, shit.

19:17.200 --> 19:18.200
Oh, shit.

19:19.010 --> 19:21.766
Well, it's every Wednesday
and we play sort of, I suppose,

19:21.886 --> 19:25.255
