The changing facilities are not too bad.

19:25.375 --> 19:28.151
- Yeah, yeah.
- All in all, it's a good thing.

19:31.704 --> 19:33.577
Right. Sit down, you two.

19:34.205 --> 19:36.329
<i>Sometimes in life you have to sit down,</i>

19:36.491 --> 19:38.541
<i>take your punishment like a man.</i>

19:39.211 --> 19:42.117
<i>Unfortunately,
this was not one of those times.</i>

19:43.890 --> 19:45.690
You've had quite a day off.

19:46.326 --> 19:48.956
You've lied to your mothers,
bought alcohol illegally,

19:49.076 --> 19:51.169
