19:51.568 --> 19:54.249
defaced the pavement outside Carli's.
Am I missing anything?

19:54.879 --> 19:56.769
We also hit a spastic with a Frisbee.

19:58.130 --> 20:00.569
- I feel totally let down, William.
- It wasn't our fault, Mum.

20:00.730 --> 20:03.464
I said to Kevin here, I thought
I brought you up better than that.

20:03.584 --> 20:05.889
- It isn't our fault.
- Why's it not your fault then?

20:07.146 --> 20:09.077
It all happened because he touched us.

20:09.197 --> 20:10.592
- What?
- Me?

20:12.893 --> 20:14.609
He touched us here,

20:15.650 --> 20:16.490
and here.

20:18.263 --> 20:19.169
And here.

20:20.794 --> 20:24.050
- The bumhole.
- You evil little shits!

20:24.504 --> 20:26.030
I'll deal with this, Kevin.

20:26.150 --> 20:28.729
Now listen to me, you two.
That is an extraordinary allegation.

20:28.891 --> 20:30.929
You should think {very }carefully
before you repeat it.

20:31.091 --> 20:33.929
- Just cos Kevin's gay doesn't mean...
- No, I'm not gay.

20:34.091 --> 20:37.249
- We're all friends, it doesn't matter.
- I'm not gay. I was married for{ nearly}...

20:37.410 --> 20:40.075
- Oscar Wilde was married.
- That is enough!

20:40.195 --> 20:43.410
- Although, he is right, Kevin...
- I'm not gay!

20:43.530 --> 20:45.021
All right, don't have a hissy fit.

20:45.141 --> 20:48.145
Just because Kevin is gay doesn't
make him automatically a paedophile.

20:48.265 --> 20:49.769
I'm not a paedophile.

20:49.931 --> 20:51.649
