Today we even talked about heroin.

21:11.532 --> 21:12.969
There's a long road ahead of us

21:13.130 --> 21:14.771
but with your support

21:14.891 --> 21:16.041
and your love

21:16.691 --> 21:17.929
we think we can make it.

21:18.258 --> 21:20.911
So please, as our parents,

21:22.689 --> 21:23.490
help us.

21:37.530 --> 21:39.018
<i>And so we were so pathetic,</i>

21:39.138 --> 21:42.911
<i>even my mum, who has no sense of humour,
was laughing at us.</i>

21:47.410 --> 21:50.529
- Hello. You look well.
